{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"background_color","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/Manifest/background_color","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"\n<ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/Manifest/background_color\">background_color</a></li></ol>\n","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"properties\">\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"row\">\n        <div class=\"warning notecard\" id=\"sect1\">\n          <p>wobuhuisuanmin</p>\n        </div>\n        <h5 id=\"type\">Type</h5>\n      </th>\n      <td><code>String</code></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"row\">Mandatory</th>\n      <td>No</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n<p>被装载其样式表之前的 <code>background_color</code> 构件限定了用于应用页的占位符的背景颜色来显示。此值用于由用户代理来绘制一个快捷方式的背景颜色，当样式表加载之前清单是可用的。</p>\n<p>（原文：The background_color member defines a placeholder background color for the application page to display before its stylesheet is loaded. This value is used by the user agent to draw the background color of a shortcut when the manifest is available before the stylesheet has loaded.）</p>\n<p>因此，<code>background_color</code> 应于 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/background-color\"><code>background-color</code></a>网站样式表中的 CSS 属性匹配，以在启动 Web 应用程序和加载网站内容之间进行平滑过渡。</p>\n<p>（原文：Therefore <code>background_color</code> should match the <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/background-color\"><code>background-color</code></a> CSS property in the site’s stylesheet for a smooth transition between launching the web application and loading the site's content.）</p>\n<div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect2\">\n  <p><strong>备注：</strong> 该 <code>background_color</code> 构件仅用于在从网络或存储介质加载主样式表时改善用户体验。<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/background-color\"><code>background-color</code></a> 当渐进式 Web 应用程序样式表可用时，用户代理不会将其用作 CSS 属性。</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"实例","title":"实例","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: json notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token property\">\"background_color\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"red\"</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"规范","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://w3c.github.io/manifest/#background_color-member","title":"Web Application Manifest"}],"query":"html.manifest.background_color"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"html.manifest.background_color","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/Manifest/background_color/bcd.json"}}],"toc":[{"text":"实例","id":"实例"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"}],"summary":"被装载其样式表之前的 background_color 构件限定了用于应用页的占位符的背景颜色来显示。此值用于由用户代理来绘制一个快捷方式的背景颜色，当样式表加载之前清单是可用的。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"background_color","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"background_color","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"background_color","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/manifest/background_color","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/manifest/background_color/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/Manifest","title":"Web App Manifest"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/Manifest/background_color","title":"background_color"}],"pageTitle":"background_color - Web App Manifest | MDN","noIndexing":false}}